<plot>In the year 2020 Britain is divided into North &amp; South. The Royal Family has been deposed and in its place rule the Knights of God, a harsh militaristic religious order headed by Prior Mordrin. But a rebel movement is growing, inspite of Mordrin's brainwashing "re-education" camps, and joining it are two love-struck teenagers, Gervase &amp; Julia, who escape from one of the camps to join a quest to find the rightful King of England, and thus re-establish democracy &amp; order to the land...</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?294679</url></doc>
